Carson Pirie Scott and Co said itsFebruary sales increased 18.2 pct to 104.3 mln dlrs from 88.2mln dlrs a year ago.    It said each of its business groups - retail foodserviceand lodging and distribution - contributed to the sales gain.    The Food Service and Lodging Group's sales were up 8.9 pctafter eliminating sales of the Steak 'n Egg Kitchen Restaurantchain sold Aug 15, 1986. Reuter&#3;